<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不能再去了。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须去！”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女人抓走了唐僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女人是个蝎子精。她很危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她确实很危险！”八戒大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她到底用什么扎的我们？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是她尾巴上的毒钩。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又想起了那疼痛的感觉，浑身打冷颤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会靠近她的。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就连佛祖都怕她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那一天，佛祖正在教导他的弟子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那蝎子爬了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想把蝎子赶走，却被它扎了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真的是非常痛！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，佛祖让侍卫抓住那蝎子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但它却逃到了凡间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空开始踱步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们要怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们必须把师父救回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去天庭找星官来帮忙吧。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，观音菩萨消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，悟空到了南天门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，悟空。”门将说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来找星官的。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门将告诉了悟空去星官宫殿的路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，悟空就到了宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他敲了宫殿的大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空。”星官说，“找我有事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要你的帮助。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在护送唐僧去西天取经，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他被一个妖怪抓走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨说你可以帮助我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星官看上去有点儿疑惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道你为什么需要我的帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我听说你很厉害的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是个什么样的妖怪？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是个蝎子精。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”星官点点头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明白了。带路吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们必须快一点儿了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空带着星官来到了凡间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们来到那座山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒还在揉自己的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“星官是来帮我们的。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星官看着八戒的鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以治好你的鼻子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒走到了星官面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星官朝着八戒的鼻子吹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那伤口立刻就好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。”八戒微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也被扎了。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但那毒钩并没有在我脑袋上留下伤口。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝着八戒咧嘴笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我比这猪厉害多了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒皱了皱眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的特殊法术可以打败那蝎子精。”星官说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们只要把她引出来就行了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家走到了洞穴前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219565</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净躲在了岩石后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空站在洞门前大叫道：“立刻放了我师父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他用最快的速度跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那女人冲出了洞穴，疯狂地旋转着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，星官变成了一只大公鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公鸡开始鸣叫，声音在山间回响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那女人尖叫着用双手捂住了耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公鸡又叫了一声，女人消失在了一阵烟雾里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>原地出现了一只死蝎子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跑进了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他找到了坐在桌边的唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧的双眼亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！谢谢你救了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空微笑了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要有我在，就不会让妖怪伤害你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个女人并不想伤害我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是想和我结婚！”唐僧叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我告诉她我是个和尚，永远不会结婚的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我唯一的目标就是去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>